=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mvt1665702861160.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mvt1665702861160.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mvt1665702861160.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mvt1665702861160\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Differences Between Static and Dynamic Server Pages\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The following table describes the differences between <span class=\"keyword\">Static and Dynamic\n         Server Pages</span>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mvt1665702861160__section_w945ab1b5b1_w946ab1b5_w947ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Differences Between Static and Dynamic Server Pages</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Issue</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">DSP</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">USP</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Notes</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Component type</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic Server Pages</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Static Server Pages</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Page Updating</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Both full page and incremental</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Full page</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Communication</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Asynchronous, using Ajax</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Synchronous, using form submit</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Layout</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Well-formatted XHTML</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Proprietary XHTML</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">For both DSPs and USPs, the layout can be maintained with the internal\n                           editor or any XHTML-compliant editor. It is also possible to store the\n                           layout in files per web page.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Binding</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Standard XHTML tags using <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attribute</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Proprietary tags using XHTML <code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code> attribute</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Derived entities and fields must be bound to elements in the server page.\n                           For more details, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zur1665702620176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zur1665702620176.html\" title=\"Binding refers to the way in which layout elements are connected to data structures and triggers in the component structure. It ensures that data is displayed by the appropriate HTML elements in the web page, and that the correct trigger is executed when data in a field is changed.\">Binding Web Layout to Component Structure</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Widgets</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Rich set of Javascript-based widgets</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Limited set of controls</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">For more details, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sno1665702583691.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sno1665702583691.html\" title=\"Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser.\">Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yjb1665702863271.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yjb1665702863271.html\" title=\"Widgets for static server pages (USPs) are HTML controls that determine how data is represented in the web page.\">Widgets for Static Server Pages</a>. </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic widget properties</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Not supported</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Interactive Triggers</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">All widgets have an OnChange extended trigger, and some have a detail trigger</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">No interactive triggers, except detail for Button control.</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">None.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Syntax checking</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Done in the browser using JavaScript</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Not supported</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">For more details, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"maf1714305172540.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/maf1714305172540.html\" title=\"Uniface always validates data before storing it to ensure that it conforms with field syntax definitions and other validation rules. However, it is also possible to have the browser check some field syntax definitions so that the user gets immediate feedback on possible data entry errors.\">Syntax Checking in Web Applications</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">JavaScript</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Requires JavaScript</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">JavaScript not required, although it can be used</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">JavaScript is used in USPs for browser-side field syntax checking, but it is possible to run a USP without this.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ProcScript</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Web and DSP-specific ProcScript</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Web-specific ProcScript</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">For more details, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xcq1665702683871.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xcq1665702683871.html\" title=\"Some ProcScript instructions are specific to web applications (including static server pages). There are also some that are unique to dynamic server pages. They are used to read data into the component, and generate responses to be sent to the client, and to activate ProcScript modules on the client or the server.\">ProcScript for Dynamic Server Pages</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uix1665702684801.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uix1665702684801.html\" title=\"Several ProcScript instructions are specific to web applications, and some other ProcScript instructions behave differently in web applications or are inapplicable.\">ProcScript for Static Server Pages</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error handling</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Must be programmed</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Must be programmed</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvt1665702861160__table_d2180e1_d2181e1_d2182e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">For more details, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqd1665702756360.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqd1665702756360.html\" title=\"Uniface always validates data before storing it to ensure that it conforms with declarative and procedural validation rules. You can customize the error handling and reporting using server-side and client-side triggers.\">Data Error Handling in Web Applications</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Differences Between Static and Dynamic Server Pages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Differences Between Static and Dynamic Server Pages The following table describes the differences between Static and Dynamic Server Pages . Table 1. Differences Between Static and Dynamic Server Pages Issue DSP USP Notes Component type Dynamic Server Pages Static Server Pages None. Page Updating Both full page and incremental Full page None. Communication Asynchronous, using Ajax Synchronous, using form submit None. Layout Well-formatted XHTML Proprietary XHTML For both DSPs and USPs, the layout can be maintained with the internal editor or any XHTML-compliant editor. It is also possible to store the layout in files per web page. Binding Standard XHTML tags using id attribute Proprietary tags using XHTML name attribute Derived entities and fields must be bound to elements in the server page. For more details, see Binding Web Layout to Component Structure . Widgets Rich set of Javascript-based widgets Limited set of controls For more details, see Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages and Widgets for Static Server Pages . Dynamic widget properties Supported Not supported None. Interactive Triggers All widgets have an OnChange extended trigger, and some have a detail trigger No interactive triggers, except detail for Button control. None. Syntax checking Done in the browser using JavaScript Not supported For more details, see Syntax Checking in Web Applications . JavaScript Requires JavaScript JavaScript not required, although it can be used JavaScript is used in USPs for browser-side field syntax checking, but it is possible to run a USP without this. ProcScript Web and DSP-specific ProcScript Web-specific ProcScript For more details, see ProcScript for Dynamic Server Pages and ProcScript for Static Server Pages . Error handling Must be programmed Must be programmed For more details, see Data Error Handling in Web Applications . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}